NUTS-2 regions in Italy.

Source: R/edashop-package.R
italy_nuts2.Rd

Simple features object with geometry of NUTS-2 regions in Italy (unprojected).

Usage

data(italy_nuts2)

Format

A simple features data frame with 21 rows and 7 variables:

NUTS_ID

NUTS-2 identifier of region

LEVL_CODE

Level of NUTS (2)

CNTR_CODE

Code of country (IT)

NUTS_NAME

Name of region

NAME_LATN

Name of region in Latin script

FID

NUTS-2 identifier of region

geometry

Geometry of regions

Source

Eurostat, retrieved with get_eurostat_geospatial

Examples

 data(italy_nuts2)
 NAME_LATN <- italy_nuts2$NAME_LATN
